thread.title: Mary Anne
thread.title_full: Maine Lobster Now reviewed by Mary Anne

author: Mary Anne
title: Mary Anne
text: Outstanding flavor and just the right seasoning for the soups. Lobster rolls were fantastic also. The only reason I did not rate this company at 5 stars is because of the OUTRAGEOUS shipping costs double more than other lobster company websites who ship frozen lobster.
